      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-mgr-tip-arc       not  = "C"            or
                     rf-mgr-cod-arc       not  = rf-cli-cod-cli or
                     rf-mgr-dat-rif       >    rr-dat-stp
                     go to  car-par-cli-300.
