           move      rf-mgr-num-doc       to   w-par-num-doc (1000)   .
           go to     car-par-cli-250.
       car-par-cli-222.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se data documento non esistente         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      rf-mgr-dat-reg       to   w-par-dat-doc (1000)   .
           move      spaces               to   w-par-num-doc (1000)   .
           go to     car-par-cli-250.
