      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        rf-mgr-dat-doc       =    zero
                     go to car-par-cli-232.
           move      rf-mgr-dat-doc       to   w-par-dat-doc (1000)   .
           move      rf-mgr-num-doc       to   w-par-num-doc (1000)   .
           go to     car-par-cli-250.
       car-par-cli-232.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
