      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se primo passaggio : uscita                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-par-flg-uno        =    spaces
                     move  "#"            to   w-par-flg-uno
                     go to car-par-cli-919.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se saldo partita a zero : uscita            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-par-sdo-par (1000) =    zero
                     go to car-par-cli-919.
